Summary: I spotted a starlike object travelling from NW to SE. My friend Jessica Dusenberry was on the phone with me and she eventually witnessed the same thing.
divs: Sighting DetailsIt was approx 9:30pm est on Wed, when i spotted a starlike object travelling from NW to SE. This object was moving in a straight line, eventually approx 20 to 30 sec later it appeared then to slowly fade away. As I lost sight of it, my friend on the phone claimed to have then picked it up. She claimed that it veared to the left, then quickly faded out. *note* This object was clearly seen under a "hazymilky" night sky.
